


        Point   -->     use told for third person sentences and said for others.




Rick : I am embarrassed.
Rick said he was embarrassed.


Nadia : My sister can't kill anyone.
Nedia told her sister couldn't kill anyone.


Josh : We are having a disscussion.
Josh said they were having a discussion.


Carol : He will confirm my message.
Carol told he would confirm her message.


Bernard : I went to exhibition yesterday.
Bernard said he went to exhibition yesterday.



Silva : My dad was anxious.
Silva told her dad wes anxious.


---------------------------------------

        Point   -->     if the speaker say something that is usual we can dont't change sentence to past.


Max : I live in California.
Max said he lives in California.
